{"tid":1975612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【極無恥】CHO屈鳩港台做完訪問先剪條問題落去","createTime":"2020-04-16T15:59:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T16:14:59.000Z","uid":229347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aa097565842876d1bf0fe142758f10ee47af8d87","tid":1975612,"uid":229347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:59:20.000Z","msg":"點解咁大單野無中文報紙講<br />\n<br />\n話說今日世衛回應之前HKFP問題，指控RTHK &lsquo;The Pulse&rsquo; 片段係經過剪接，果個鬼佬醫生唔係咁意思，仲話條問題係之後剪落去，企圖屈鳩港台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//RTHK re-shot the interviewer and questions afterwards and edited the interview in a way that created substantial distortion and misrepresentation//<br />\n<br />\n文中仲有話係醫生打番俾港台，但係港台已經答左HKFP記者話CHO講大話<br />\n<br />\n堂堂國際組織，學哂鄰國啲無恥抹黑講大話賤招 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原link： <a href=\"https://hongkongfp.com/2020/04/16/hong-kong-broadcaster-rejects-who-claim-that-interview-with-top-doctor-was-distorted/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhongkongfp.com%2F2020%2F04%2F16%2Fhong-kong-broadcaster-rejects-who-claim-that-interview-with-top-doctor-was-distorted%2F&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10NLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=f8e6a341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hongkongfp.com/2020/04/16/hong-kong-broadcaster-rejects-who-claim-that-interview-with-top-doctor-was-distorted/</a>"},{"pid":"8fce1d54115c29141efb8214d66fdc751a10e2d7","tid":1975612,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:00:39.000Z","msg":"睇唔明， 推左先"},{"pid":"f054b065420fe40e275dd7ea295ee4416b47de41","tid":1975612,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:01:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Twitter 國際戰線<br />\n</strong></